title: UFYB 4: People Pleasing
itunes:title: People Pleasing
description:
This week, we're talking about how our society and upbringing has affected our subconscious (and conscious) thinking to constantly engage in people pleasing. Join us as I explain why we often choose to prioritize others’ wants and needs over our own and the detrimental effects this has on our personal and professional lives.

Get full show notes and more information here: http://bit.ly/2AKodlm
